summary: Good Omens Trailer Thee angel Aziraphale (Michael Sheen) and the demon Crowley (David Tennant) are two unlikely friends trying...
caption:
Good Omens Trailer

Thee angel Aziraphale (Michael Sheen) and the demon Crowley (David Tennant) are two unlikely friends trying to stop the coming Armageddon. After all, they’ve grown quite fond of the Earth. Oh, and someone has misplaced the child Anti-Christ, so that’s a problem.

Good Omens, based on the novel by Neil Gaiman and Terry Pratchett, hits Amazon Prime on May 31, 2019.

blog.name: uglywettiewrites
blog.title: Infinite Chaos, locked in 1.71 meters of flesh
blog.description:
Stoking the thirst since 2016. 
Proud tertiagenarian. Switch in every sense. 18+ only, please. I blog things that make me laugh. Or cry. Or thirst. I post in spurts, so check my archive if you want to stay abreast of my bursts of sparkling wit. I also write words about David Tennant's characters. Poetry. Original fiction. Mostly naughty. All nice.

body:
Want more DT fic?

I know that since the purge, it’s nearly impossible to find anything with the search function.

If, in your casual Tumbling, you read something of mine and you’d like more but the search comes up empty, fear not.

There’s so much more!

So much.

My Masterlist: uglywettiewrites.tumblr.com/MASTERLIST

Just copy/paste to your browser for ALL the writing challenges, drabbles, fiction, and even two multi-chapter fics*.

My Ao3 link is there as well.

Head’s up - there are even more words. Go to my page and type fan fiction in the search. There’s a bunch of one-off flash fics, requests, and other hidden gems.

* Most of my fiction is crisp, tart lemons. Please read responsibly.
